type="local"
href="jms-0032.xml"
addr="jms-0032"
title="Exponentiable object">exponentiable</fr:link> when viewed as an object of the slice category <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[{\mathcal {C}}_{/B}]]></fr:tex>.</fr:p></fr:mainmatter><fr:backmatter><fr:tree
